            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-center"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 text-danger"><path d="M18 6 6 18"></path><path d="m6 6 12 12"></path></svg>Foods, drugs, or cosmetics</li>
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-center"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 text-danger"><path d="M18 6 6 18"></path><path d="m6 6 12 12"></path></svg>Household chemicals</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mb-4">You acknowledge that the products have not been tested for safety or efficacy in food, drug, medical device, cosmetic, commercial or any other use.</p>

          <h2 class="mb-3">3. Purchaser Representations</h2>
          <p>By purchasing from PeptideResearch.eu, you represent and warrant that:</p>
          <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-center"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 text-color"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>You are at least 18 years of age.</li>
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>You are affiliated with a research institution, laboratory, or are a qualified researcher.</li>
            <li class="mb-2 d-flex align-items-start"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="mr-2 mt-1 text-color flex-shrink-0"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline></svg>You are aware of the health and safety hazards associated with handling research chemicals.</li>
